Chef Wanted with Anne Burrell - Season 3, Episode 10




Showdown on the 70th Floor

Cite has been Chicago's premiere destination for romantic dining and spectacular views. With their Executive Chef retiring after nearly 30 years, the owners implore Anne Burrell to bring in four qualified candidates to take over the kitchen and modernize their classic menu.




Original Air Date: 03-Oct-2013
